---
import { Carrousel } from './react/Carrousel'
import techs from '../data/technologies.json'
---

<section class='w-full mx-auto pt-14 pb-10'>
  <h2
    id='techs'
    class='text-6xl movil-lg:text-7xl tablet-lg:text-8xl laptop:text-9xl font-bold font-inter text-white text-center my-12 movil-lg:my-16 tablet:my-16 mb-16'
  >
    Tecnologias
  </h2>

  <section class='flex flex-col items-center'>
    <!-- carrousel  -->

    <Carrousel title='Grupos de tecnologias que utilizo' client:visible qty={3}>
      <!-- HTML CSS JS -->
      <article
        class={`w-11/12 h-full flex flex-col justify-center items-center snap-center shrink-0`}
      >
        <img src='/assets/html_css_js.png' alt='git and github' />
        <p
          class='text-center text-2xl movil-lg:text-3xl laptop:text-4xl my-5 px-5 text-slate-300 font-semibold cursor-default'
        >
          HTML5, CSS & JS como tecnologias base de lado del FrontEnd.
        </p>
      </article>

      <!-- REACT, NEXTJS, ASTRO -->
      <article
        class={`w-11/12 h-full flex flex-col justify-center items-center snap-center shrink-0`}
      >
        <div class='w-full flex justify-evenly px-4'>
          <img
            class='min-w-[40px] object-contain'
            src='/assets/react_logo.png'
            alt='git and github'
          />
          <img
            class='min-w-[40px] object-contain'
            src='/assets/1200px-Nextjs-logo.svg.png'
            alt='git and github'
          />
          <img
            class='min-w-[40px] object-contain'
            src='/assets/astro-logo-B3B4DABB0A-seeklogo.com.png'
            alt='git and github'
          />
        </div>
        <p
          class='text-center text-2xl movil-lg:text-3xl laptop:text-4xl my-5 px-5 text-slate-300 font-bold cursor-default'
        >
          React, NextJs y Astro para crear aplicaciones y paginas web
          profesionales desde pequeños a grandes proyectos.
        </p>
      </article>

      <!-- NodeJs ExpressJs Socket.io -->
      <article
        class={`w-11/12 h-full flex flex-col justify-center items-center snap-center shrink-0`}
      >
        <div class='w-full flex justify-evenly px-4'>
          <img
            class='min-w-[40px] object-contain'
            src='/assets/node-js-736399_960_720-2.png'
            alt='nodejs and expressjs'
          />
          <img
            class='min-w-[40px] object-contain'
            src='/assets/socket.webp'
            alt='git and github'
          />
        </div>
        <p
          class='text-center text-2xl movil-lg:text-3xl laptop:text-4xl my-5 px-5 text-slate-300 font-bold cursor-default'
        >
          En el BackEnd utilizo NodeJS y expressJS para el procesamiento de
          datos y la comunicacion con el FrontEnd. Socket.io para la
          comunicacion en tiempo real (chat, notificaciónes)
        </p>
      </article>
      <!-- MongoDB Firebase -->
      <article
        class={`w-11/12 h-full flex flex-col justify-center items-center snap-center shrink-0 `}
      >
        <div class='w-full flex-col flex items-center'>
          <img
            class='w-52 max-h-[110px]'
            src='/assets/1 doAg1_fMQKWFoub-6gwUiQ.png'
            alt='mongob'
          />
          <img
            class='min-w-[40px] max-h-[60px]'
            src='/assets/logo-firebase.png'
            alt='firebaseb'
          />
        </div>
        <p
          class='text-center text-2xl movil-lg:text-3xl laptop:text-4xl my-5 px-5 text-slate-300 font-bold cursor-default'
        >
          Utilizo Firebase y MongoDB como Bases de Datos NoSql para gestionar
          los datos que se envian entre el frontend y el backend.
        </p>
      </article>
      <!-- GIT GITHUB -->
      <article
        class={`w-11/12 h-full flex flex-col justify-center items-center snap-center shrink-0 py-10`}
      >
        <img class='py-14' src='/assets/git_github.png' alt='git and github' />
        <p
          class='text-center text-2xl movil-lg:text-3xl laptop:text-4xl my-5 px-5 text-slate-300 font-bold cursor-default'
        >
          git y github para el vercionamiento y gestion en la nube de los
          proyectos que realizo.
        </p>
      </article>
    </Carrousel>
  </section>
  <p
    class='text-center text-4xl movil-lg:text-5xl tablet:text-6xl laptop:text-7xl font-inter font-bold mt-20 mb-10 laptop:mt-28 text-indigo-100'
  >
    Todas las tecnologias
  </p>
  <section
    class='grid grid-cols-1 movil-lg:grid-cols-2 tablet:grid-cols-3 gap-5 w-fullp-3 max-w-4xl tablet-lg:max-w-5xl px-2 mx-auto'
  >
    {
      techs.map((tech) => (
        <div class='flex items-center justify-evenly flex-wrap w-full max-w-md my-2 p-5 tablet-lg:py-7 laptop:py-8 mx-auto rounded-lg bg-gray-800 cursor-default'>
          <img
            class='max-w-[40px] max-h-[40px] laptop:max-w-[50px] laptop:max-h-[50px]'
            src={tech.image}
            alt={tech.name}
          />
          <p class='mx-5 font-inter font-semibold text-white'>{tech.name}</p>
        </div>
      ))
    }
  </section>
</section>
